      "instruction": "<p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p><p>Combine your<strong> rice vinegar</strong> with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> in a large bowl</p><p>Add your<strong> carrot & cabbage slaw mix</strong> to the bowl with the <strong>spring onion </strong>and give it a gentle mix up – this is your<strong> slaw</strong></p>",
